uk.co.strangeskies.text.properties

Class LocalizedRuntimeException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • java.lang.RuntimeException
          • uk.co.strangeskies.text.properties.LocalizedRuntimeException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GraphException, PropertyLoaderException, ReflectionException, ServiceWiringException

    public abstract class LocalizedRuntimeException
extends RuntimeException
    A localized runtime exception class. Exception messages are more frequently for developers than for users, so the message returned by Throwable.getMessage() should always be in the developer's language, which is assumed to be English by default. Constructor overloads are provided for developers to specify a different development language.
